lead_paragraph: Katie Hempen scored 11 points and No. 9 Arizona State held on late to win its seventh in a row, defeating Southern California 50-45 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Katie Hempen Leads No. 9 Arizona State Past USC 50-45
